org.gearvrf

Class GVRStockPostEffectShaderId

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gearvrf.GVRPostEffectShaderId
      • org.gearvrf.GVRStockPostEffectShaderId

  • public class GVRStockPostEffectShaderId
extends GVRPostEffectShaderId
    Represents a stock post effect shader. You get these from GVRPostEffect.GVRPostEffectShaderType; you can pass these to GVRPostEffect.GVRPostEffect(GVRContext, GVRPostEffectShaderId) and to GVRPostEffect.setShaderType(GVRPostEffectShaderId); you can not pass these to GVRPostEffectShaderManager.getShaderMap(GVRCustomPostEffectShaderId).
